channel.description: So I cant find any on google and was wondering if anyone has a developer pic i can use for my forum. Like, I want to put it as the rank picture. See where the stars are under your name? I wanted a pic that says "developer" but cant find one anywhere. Anyone?

Only bad thing since I have switched to Linux is that I can’t use photoshop. GIMP is really good don’t get me wrong, but I’m just not used to it yet.
